레스토랑 도착 We'll be waiting for someone.
레스토랑 도착 Somebody else is coming.

phrases.phrase: 친구 한 명이 곧 올 겁니다.
meanings: 레스토랑 도착 A friend is coming soon.
레스토랑 도착 A friend will join me shortly.

vlive.korean: [휴닝카이 미워] 왜 그런 멘트를 한 거야...
vlive.english: [Hate you, HUENINGKAI] Why did you say things like that?

vlive.korean: 어떻게 한 거야? - 야 가족사진 같다 되게!
vlive.english: How did you do that? - Hey! This looks like a family picture.

vlive.korean: 아이씨! 아 얘 일부러 한 거야!
vlive.english: Come on! They did that on purpose!

vlive.korean: 왜 이렇게 연결이 자꾸 불안정 한 거야?

examples.english: What the blazes have you done?

examples.korean: 너 지금 정말 멍청한 짓을 한 거야!
examples.english: You’ve really gone and done it now!

examples.korean: “너 무슨 짓을 한 거야?” 엘리가 불안해하며 외쳤다.
examples.english: ‘What have you done?’ Ellie cried in alarm.

examples.korean: 넌 어째서 어머니를 그렇게 화나시게 한 거야?
examples.english: Why did you have to go and upset your mother like that?

examples.korean: 저 낙서들 좀 봐. 그 녀석들이 또 저 짓을 한 거야.
examples.english: Look at all that graffiti—those kids have been at it again.
